      "href": "/elleofwands/list/dirtbag-cinema/",
      "user": "elleofwands",
      "slug": "dirtbag-cinema",
      "title": "dirtbag cinema",
      "desc": "this is just a descriptor i use for certain movies and in doing so i accidentally convinced people it was an actual film movement\n\nso behold, DIRTBAG CINEMA:\n-made in the 70s (this is important. the 60s still have a shadow of the hays code and the 80s get too polished. must be made in the 70s, the prime Dirtbag Era)\n-also takes place in the 70s. no period or futuristic shit\n-involves shitty men doing shitty things\n-no woman has more than ten minutes of screentime\n-film grain and brown tones off the charts\n-usually gangster, crime, and/or action-focused\n-takes place in the city. in the STREETS!!!\n-setting feels grimy and dirty\n-amoral male protagonist. usually he’s a cop… more",
      "owner": "List by elle",
      "tags": []
