      "href": "/lintonfellows/list/prestige-dirtbag-cinema/",
      "user": "lintonfellows",
      "slug": "prestige-dirtbag-cinema",
      "title": "Prestige Dirtbag Cinema",
      "desc": "This list is an attempt to grapple with the term “Prestige Dirtbag Cinema,” or Prestige Dirtbag Movies, or PDC. The Big Picture Podcast introduced me to the concept of this being a genre, and it resonated with me. I knew intuitively that a lot of my favorite movies fit that bill. But what is Prestige Dirtbag Cinema? What movies make up the PDC canon? What are the unifying themes, techniques, and filmmakers? That’s my project here, and I would love your input. \n\nNothing is set in stone on this list, I will be updating in response to comments. Switch view to list mode to see the notes I’ve made on certain movies that I would consider borderline. \n\nNow some thoughts on what… more",
